oh there isn't that much change. In `variants/heltec_esp32c3/pins_arduino.h`:  ```-static const uint8_t SDA = 1;
-static const uint8_t SCL = 0;
+static const uint8_t SDA = 18;
+static const uint8_t SCL = 19;```
and in `variants/heltec_esp32c3/variant.h`:```-#define BUTTON_PIN 9
+//#define BUTTON_PIN 9
-#define LED_PIN 2      // LED
+//#define LED_PIN 2      // LED```
that's it

